{"tid":569407,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"玩家網上買機被騙　籲網民助「起底」尋騙徒","createTime":"2018-02-22T16:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T17:45:58.000Z","uid":2323,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bb740c4c6ab28dc45182ae900954ffdc7f7e7697","tid":569407,"uid":2323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T16:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/001430_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F001430_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=3367a27e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「準獵人」買機玩「芒亨」慘被騙！近期PS4遊戲「魔物獵人」獲全城熱棒，不少機迷不眠不休「屠龍」，甚至有人為此遊戲特意買機支持，以致傳出PS4一度缺貨的消息。一名港男更在買機時慘墮騙局，據了解，他近日透過一個網上交易平台，以3,000港元向一名賣家，購買PS4 Pro MHW特別版連遊戲碟，相約於上周六（17日）在港鐵太子站內交收被騙。<br />\n<br />\n事主在網上留言稱，當時現身的賣家為一名年約18歲的青年，當時對方要求「先畀錢後驗貨」，事主遂照做交付3,000港元現金，惟欲留住對方驗機時，「佢封晒所有膠袋同箱，而且面有難色，我就Dup低頭拆箱，當時我喺閘外佢喺閘內，隔離係一條樓梯，短短幾秒，我抬起頭就唔見咗佢，即刻跨過站都已經追唔到。」<br />\n<br />\n事主拆開包裝箱查看，發現裡面只有一部過時、估計現時只值數百港元的舊版PS3，始知自己受騙，遂往警署報警求助，Madam亦曾致電懷疑騙徒，他指：「電話Madam係打得通，仲有對話，點知（對方）一聽到係警署（打嚟）就收咗線。」事主又公開騙徒的電話號碼及網上帳戶，呼籲網民一起「起底」尋人。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，事主今次購買的是今年一月最新推出的特別版PS4 Pro，現時全新售價約為5,500至6,000港元。至於懷疑涉案騙徒，他除出售該PS4外，亦出售一條標價1,700港元的LV名牌皮帶，以及各種遊戲禮品劵等。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，旺角警署有接獲相關報案，警方正積極進行調查，東網正向警察公共關係科查詢詳情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/001500_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F001500_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=2fac3ba0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/23/001503_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F23%2F001503_799bad5a3b514f096e69bbc4a7896cd9.jpg&h=ab8d0fc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180222/bkn-20180222225313996-0222_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180222%2Fbkn-20180222225313996-0222_00822_001.html&d=ZRIXzU2NY6P31ttKCpkdv0zHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=bc1e21cc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180222/bkn-20180222225313996-0222_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d24e2e8e44b7253c46d9ef568469891eb72127e1","tid":569407,"uid":2323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T16:16:10.000Z","msg":"ps3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d693aefb37f6e5658cbd43b0a4440aec53527b3","tid":569407,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T16:17:58.000Z","msg":"警犬咁鬼垃圾嘅，有電話都捉唔到人？"},{"pid":"4c3f2dc27dc33d869b7b82ba6dc4072a189bac16","tid":569407,"uid":2323,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0d693aefb37f6e5658cbd43b0a4440aec53527b3","tid":569407,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T16:17:58.000Z","msg":"警犬咁鬼垃圾嘅，有電話都捉唔到人？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T16:20:10.000Z","msg":"警犬打人就識 邊識捉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a870b9416cb86d5426b49d4fe05bc7c482a2755","tid":569407,"uid":5026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T16:20:40.000Z","msg":"又上黎偷料"},{"pid":"ee5687ee9ac71741a6a09c765797a9c8bd9b6b6c","tid":569407,"uid":123264,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c3f2dc27dc33d869b7b82ba6dc4072a189bac16","tid":569407,"uid":2323,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0d693aefb37f6e5658cbd43b0a4440aec53527b3","tid":569407,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T16:17:58.000Z","msg":"警犬咁鬼垃圾嘅，有電話都捉唔到人？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T16:20:10.000Z","msg":"警犬打人就識 邊識捉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"h